latestPosts.caption:
We all heard at some point people saying “once you leave home, it will never be the same” yes I agree. But the beauty about it is — you can have multiple “home”. 

We grow we move we learn we explore we experience we change. And as we go through all of that it is a privilege to consider different places “home” 

So keep exploring, keep learning, keep growing and don’t limit yourself to just being one thing. We are meant to outgrow ourselves but — What a blessing to see yourself grow 🤍

Grateful to consider Vancouver and bukidnon as my home. If you made it this far reading this caption — thank you friends and family for making both of these places “home” to me. Love you all!
Who said you can’t wear your pj’s outside? 🤭
